dispose

public void dispose()
             throws CAException
This call will dispose the underlying CoreAudio object that is associated with the CAJava object. After this call the CAJava object is no longer usable and will throw CARuntimeExceptions to indicate that the CAJava object's native object has been disposed.

Throws:
